#ROOM
Vnum     39052
Name     &WNorthern Entrance from Feralas&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     The lush greenery of Feralas is left behind as you step into a 
blinding white desert. The air is dry and tastes of dust and 
ancient things. Massive cliffs of white sandstone rise on either 
side of the narrow pass, and the wind howls between the rocks 
like a dying animal. A wide, sand-swept road leads south toward 
the center of the wastes.
~
#EXIT
Direction out~
ToRoom    37101
Desc      Return to the southern pass in Feralas.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    39053
Desc      The path leads into the Silithus desert.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 39005 5 39052
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     39053
Name     &WThe Shifting Sands - North&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     Flat, white plains stretch out in every direction. The glare of 
the sun is intense, making it difficult to see more than a few 
hundred yards. Small dust-devils dance across the dunes, 
kicking up fine white silt that coats everything in a layer of 
grit.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    39052
Desc      The northern entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    39054
Desc      The road continues south.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    39058
Desc      A trail leads toward the Crystal Vale.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 39018 5 39053
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     39054
Name     &WThe High Desert Road&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     A wide road marked by large stone pillars. To the south, the 
towers of a major outpost are visible against the horizon. 
Silithid workers can be seen scurrying across the dunes, 
carrying bits of chitin and bone toward the east.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    39053
Desc      Northern Shifting Sands.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    39061
Desc      Entrance to Cenarion Hold.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    39055
Desc      Toward the Twilight Base Camp.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 39003 5 39054
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     39055
Name     &mTwilight Base Camp - Entrance&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     A cluster of purple and black tents built in the shadow of a 
large, red crystal formation. Twilight cultists move with 
religious intensity, ignoring the heat of the desert.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    39054
Desc      Return to the road.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    39056
Desc      The inner camp.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 39001 5 39055
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     39056
Name     &mTwilight Base Camp - Inner Circle&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     The center of the cultist camp. A large, smoking brazier burns 
in the middle of a ritual circle drawn in the sand. 
Geologists work to extract power from the nearby crystals.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    39055
Desc      The camp entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    39057
Desc      The Overlord's Tent.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 39002 5 39056
Reset O 0 39031 5 39056
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     39057
Name     &mTent of the Twilight Overlord&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A large, well-furnished tent filled with dark artifacts and 
encrypted scrolls. The air inside is heavy with the scent 
of burning incense and shadow magic.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    39056
Desc      The inner circle.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 39016 1 39057
  Reset G 1 39038 1
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     39058
Name     &WThe Crystal Vale - Entry&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     A shallow valley filled with towering shards of red and blue 
crystal. The air here hums with magical energy, and the 
ground is covered in fine crystalline dust.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    39053
Desc      Return to the sands.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    39059
Desc      Deep into the vale.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 39008 5 39058
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     39059
Name     &WThe Crystal Vale - Heart&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     The center of the valley is dominated by a single crystal 
shard of immense size. It pulses with a rhythmic, low-
frequency sound that can be felt in the marrow of your 
bones. Shattered rock elementals roam the area.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    39058
Desc      The vale entry.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    39060
