#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 39008 10 39059
Reset O 0 39035 10 39059
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     39060
Name     &WThe Abyssal Templar's Spire&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     A high stone platform built into the valley wall. A 
massive elemental templar stands guard here, protecting 
the most potent crystal formations.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    39059
Desc      The vale heart.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 39022 1 39060
  Reset G 1 39028 1
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     39061
Name     &GCenarion Hold - North Gate&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    ~
Desc     The primary entrance to the Cenarion Circle's desert 
stronghold. Two high stone towers flank the gate, and 
sentinels watch the road from the ramparts. The air 
here is significantly cooler, thanks to the magic 
emanating from the hold's central moonwell.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    39054
Desc      The desert road.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    39062
Desc      Cenarion Hold Plaza.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 39000 5 39061
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     39062
Name     &GCenarion Hold - Town Plaza&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    ~
Desc     The heart of the hold is busy with druids and warriors 
from all races. A beautiful moonwell sits in the center 
of the square, and several large stone buildings provide 
shelter, trade, and tactical planning.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    39061
Desc      The north gate.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
