Name     &GThe Druid's Rest&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A warm, quiet inn filled with the scent of pine and 
sweetgrass. Leather-bound books and dried herbs line 
the walls, providing a peaceful retreat from the desert.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    39062
Desc      The plaza.~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     39064
Name     &GCenarion Hold - Flight Roost&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    ~
Desc     A high stone ledge overlooking the northern sands. Several 
gryphons and hippogryphs rest here, ready to carry 
travelers across the continent.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    39062
Desc      The plaza.~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     39065
Name     &GThe Cenarion Commander's Hall&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The primary military building in the hold. Tactical maps 
of the silithid hives are pinned to the walls, and 
General Andorov can often be seen here reviewing reports.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    39062
Desc      The plaza.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 39015 1 39065
#ENDROOM

